node.text: The reason we are all here in Italy is because of this incredible woman. Her heart, her smile, her strength, her journey, her story…. I can go on and on about @tembilocke but today, and everyday she holds court like the Queen that she is, and she can and will certainly speak for herself. So on her birthday, as a gift to her, read her book From Scratch. Trust me, you won’t regret it. And wait for our show next year. Happy birthday to a true super hero who’s strength is LOVE, love and more love!!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Zoe Saldana on July 17, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Learn about the situation Educate yourself on what is happening in Cuba. After 62 years, Cuban's are not protesting because of a lack of vaccines or the embargo as some sources are reporting. They're protesting to obtain freedom from a government that has starved, killed, and censored them for six decades.'.

Since July 11, it has been emotionally and mentally taxing on Cubans, especially the diaspora, to see on such a wide scale the suffering of our people. Not knowing how our families are doing and having to see videos and photos of our people being beaten and taken away by the government to join the military against their will.'.

Ask your Cuban friends questions about why this is happening, share their stories on your platforms and don't ignore something that is happening 90 miles from the U.S. coastline.'.
